text: Ukhnaagiin Khurelsukh (, born 14 June 1968) is a Mongolian politician. In October 2017 he became the Prime Minister of Mongolia, he was Prime Minister until January 2021. He became the President of Mongolia in June 2021. He was elected to the Parliament of Mongolia three times – in 2000, 2004 and 2012. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Current national leaders Category:Prime Ministers of Mongolia Category:People from Ulaanbaatar
